methods.name: init
methods.desc: Deploy the contract and set the caller as admin.

methods.name: set_validator
methods.desc: Admin assigns a validator address for project reviews.

methods.name: transfer_admin
methods.desc: Admin transfers ownership to a new admin account.

methods.name: ensure_token
methods.desc: Create the AARNA ASA if it doesn't exist. Returns the ASA ID.

methods.name: submit_project
methods.desc: Developer submits a new project. Returns the project index.

methods.name: approve_project
methods.desc: Validator approves a project and assigns a credit amount.

methods.name: issue_credits
methods.desc:
Validator issues AARNA tokens to submitter.
Status: 2 (verified) → 4 (issued). Prevents double-issuance.

methods.name: list_for_sale
methods.desc:
List AARNA tokens for sale using clawback to escrow.
Returns the listing index.

methods.name: buy_listing
methods.desc: Buy tokens from a listing. Transfers tokens to buyer and ALGO to seller.

methods.name: cancel_listing
methods.desc: Seller cancels their listing. Escrowed tokens returned.
